description: The UK government has said a new mutation of the coronavirus is ‚Äúout of control‚Äù in parts of England and spreading rapidly.   The latest figures show more than 35,000 new infections, many in London and the south-east.Several countries have announced that they are banning travel from the UK ‚Äî with France suspending passenger and some freight transport.  The Port of Dover has temporarily been closed. New restrictions have come into force for 18 million people in England and 3 million people in Wales. In England areas within the new Tier 4 rules include London, Kent and most of Essex.  People have been told to stay home with  non-essential shops closed.   Christmas mixing of households will not be permitted.
